item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Beyoncé - Cowboy Carter Vinyl/CD rip
item.description:
Hi Guys. Does Someone Have a Vinyl or CD (or both) rip version of Beyoncé's ACT II: COWBOY CARTER in flac? (Like... the "ACT II: BEYINCÉ" edition).
I've Heard it has different mixes from the digital one.

"AMERIICAN REQUIEM" has different lyric verse.
"PROTECTOR" has no children noise at the end.
"JOLENE" has extra Willie Jones ad-libs at the end.
"LEVII'S JEANS" has a different transition.
"DESERT EAGLE" has a slightly different intro.
"RIIVERDANCE"; "II HANDS II HEAVENS" and "TYRANT" has a slightly longer length version.
